<div><head>《曹毗志怪》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.2">漢武鑿昆明池，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.3">極深，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.4">悉是灰墨，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.5">無復土。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.6">舉朝不解。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.7">以問東方朔。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.8">朔曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.9">「臣愚不足以知之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.10">可試問西域胡人。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.11">帝以朔不知，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.12">難以移問。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.13">至後漢明帝時，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.14">外國道人入來洛陽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.15">時有憶方朔言者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.16">乃試以武帝時灰墨問之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.17">胡人云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.18">」天地大劫將盡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.19">則劫燒；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.20">此劫燒之餘。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.21">乃知朔言有旨。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.22">《初學記》七。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.23">《草堂詩記箋》二十六。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.24">又三十八有末六字，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1506_CHANT_001-1a.25">乃作「方旨作驗」。<lb/></seg>
</p>
